_json.gridTitle: Beyond Good Looks: Add Value and Style to Your Home with This One Element
_json.description: Plantation shutters are a hallmark of Southern style that are also a great choice for window coverings in homes of almost any style. The deep-louvered, swinging wooden shutters provide a sophisticated alternative to blinds and will give any home a little touch of the genteel.
